  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dba\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c 03\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Catches 03 with ice",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Badulla Senior Superintendent of Police Mr. Sujith Vedamulla has arrested three suspects with 13 grams and 750 milligram of ice drug in an operation carried out by the officers of the Badulla Divisional Criminal Investigation Division in the early morning of today (17th) in Badulla Veeryapura area.",
        "Thirty thousand five hundred rupees in cash, a digital scale, two mobile phones and ganja were seized from the suspects today.",
        "The police say that the arrested suspects belong to the age groups of 25, 26, and 35 years old and belong to the Pidanchis of Haliyala, Kailagoda and Veeryapura."
      ],
